WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The reason people resist change in a lot of circumstances seems to not be because they don't want to change, or they don't see the value.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:16.000
It seems to be a lot more around, I have a lot of other things to do, and this is the worst thing on my list, and it's not going to help me, it's going to help someone else later.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:29.000
So, giving them tools that make it really easy for them to document, or make it really easy for them to share, or even if it's just having a common storage location where you can go find it later and deal with it, I think really helps along the process.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:38.000
And that, to me, has gotten a lot further than trying to really get people to rethink the way that they work, which is a much longer term, harder thing to transition through.

